@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About Us — PDFToolstack</PageTitle>

<div class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">

        <div class="legal-header">
            <h1>About PDFToolstack</h1>
            <p class="legal-date">Free PDF Tools for Everyone</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-content">

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    PDFToolstack was built with one simple goal —
                    to give everyone access to powerful PDF tools
                    without paywalls, forced signups, or
                    confusing software downloads. Every tool on
                    our platform is free, fast, and works
                    directly in your browser.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>What We Build</h2>
                <p>
                    We are a growing suite of free online PDF
                    tools covering everything you need to work
                    with documents — compression, conversion,
                    merging, form filling, redaction, and much
                    more. Our platform is built by developers
                    who believe great tools should be accessible
                    to everyone.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>Your Privacy First</h2>
                <p>
                    We built PDFToolstack with privacy at its
                    core. Every file you upload is processed
                    securely and automatically deleted within
                    1 hour. We never read, analyze, or sell the
                    contents of your documents. Your files are
                    yours.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>Our Technology</h2>
                <p>
                    PDFToolstack is built on modern, enterprise-
                    grade technology including ASP.NET Core,
                    Blazor WebAssembly, and Microsoft Azure —
                    the same infrastructure trusted by Fortune
                    500 companies. This means fast processing,
                    reliable uptime, and bank-grade security
                    for your documents.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>Always Improving</h2>
                <p>
                    We are constantly adding new tools and
                    improving existing ones based on user
                    feedback. Have a suggestion or need a tool
                    we don't offer yet? We'd love to hear from
                    you.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
                <p>
                    We love hearing from our users. Whether you
                    have feedback, a feature request, or just
                    want to say hello — reach out to us at
                    <a href="mailto:hello@pdftoolstack.com">
                        hello@pdftoolstack.com
                    </a> or visit our
                    <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
                </p>
            </section>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>